Requirements
------------

On Ubuntu 12.04 we need git and boto:
$ apt-get install git
$ apt-get install python-dev python-pip
$ pip install --upgrade pip

If doesn't work logout and sudo again:
$ pip install --upgrade virtualenv
$ pip install --upgrade boto

This is all it takes to backup all non-root volumes:
$ cd /root
$ git clone git@github.com:9apps/9tk.git && cd 9tk/backups
$ python backup.py setup